00:00:18,958 --> 00:00:22,666
- Narrator: THIS IS THE
BEAUTIFUL TOWN OF HARGEON.

2
00:00:22,750 --> 00:00:24,500
AND THOSE SAILS IN THE DISTANCE

3
00:00:24,583 --> 00:00:28,875
BELONG TO A FAIRY TAIL SHIP
THAT RECENTLY DEPARTED ITS PORT.

4
00:00:28,958 --> 00:00:32,333
IT CARRIES 16 EAGER AND
ADVENTUROUS YOUNG WIZARDS

5
00:00:32,416 --> 00:00:35,958
WHO ARE ON THEIR WAY
TO TENROU ISLAND.

6
00:00:37,458 --> 00:00:39,333
- ( theme music playing )

