14
00:01:08,208 --> 00:01:09,916
( singing in Japanese )

15
00:01:31,250 --> 00:01:33,541
♪ MY PERFECT DREAM! ♪

16
00:01:41,083 --> 00:01:43,000
- Chorus: ♪ YEAH, YEAH, YEAH ♪

